%% Diagram: Persistence Flow Journal Checkpoint Recovery
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant MP as Multiplayer<br/>(Rust)
    participant J as Journal<br/>(DynamoDB)
    participant S as Checkpoint<br/>(S3)

    Note over C,MP: Steady-state edits
    C->>MP: delta @ ~33ms
    MP->>MP: apply, assign seq #

    par Journal
        MP->>J: append (~0.5s)
        J-->>MP: ack (~600ms)
    and Checkpoint
        MP->>S: snapshot (30-60s)
        S-->>MP: ack
    end

    Note over MP: Crash, new process recovers
    MP->>S: load checkpoint
    S-->>MP: snapshot @ seq=N
    MP->>J: read seq > N
    J-->>MP: deltas N+1 ... M
    MP->>MP: replay to seq=M

    Note over MP,J: Loss < 1s vs 60s checkpoint-only
